Venue: Lecture Room 2, Sha Tin Town Hall, 1 Yuen Wo Road, Sha Tin, New Territories The seminars will be conducted in Cantonese. Seats will be allocated on a first-come, first-served basis. Members of the public who would like to attend any of the seminars should register at www.jcecc.hk/sem2019. Walk-in registration will only be accepted subject to availability of seats. For enquiries, please call 3509 8765.
